{"tid":671201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人執到個深藍色長形銀包","createTime":"2018-05-20T02:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T03:09:35.000Z","uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8cd1885c44c01d88974de6940d721136e87b856","tid":671201,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:52:04.000Z","msg":"大概琴日上午10點到11點到，我去緊鑽石山親戚屋企，買咗菠蘿包諗住做早餐，喺佢樓下球場嘅長凳坐低咗，起身走時唔記得拎翻袋包同銀包，有冇人拾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有嘅麻煩交去警署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者聯絡我，拜託。 入面有哂證件，銀行卡同50蚊，同有好有紀念價值嘅嘢，唔該曬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/104955_69b7790f540ee42497ddc53524da23f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F104955_69b7790f540ee42497ddc53524da23f2.png&h=4ae76efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概喺咁嘅大細，顏色喺相中嘅藍色，全藍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有請聯絡我tg: <a href=\"https://t.me/ken1123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fken1123&d=z7vz%2BB42COkwiY3XNLusEARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=82a76cbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ken1123</a><br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"5564b7a29a09603088a24a7021907be95367ecc2","tid":671201,"uid":44902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"沙津袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d8f39db63690079f1e278db90bc3a22a44e70a","tid":671201,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5564b7a29a09603088a24a7021907be95367ecc2","tid":671201,"uid":44902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"沙津袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif